data.description: Lovely 4 BR, 2 BA brick home in the popular Southern Hills Subdivision of Medina. The master bedroom also has a sitting area/office. Two car garage, fenced back yard, partially covered patio, walk in attic, eat in kitchen with breakfast area, separate laundry room, formal dining room, living room with hardwood floors & a gas log fireplace. New stainless appliances. Over 2100 htd. sq ft.
